data.title: The Songs of Paul Dresser; With an Introduction by His Brother Theodore Dreiser
data.meta_description: New York: Boni and Liveright, 1927. First Edition. 4to, 263pp; patterned blue cloth with tan cloth spine. Slight lean; small scratch to front board; very good in an edge worn dust jacket. Item #205715 Compendium of music and lyrics, illustrated with stereopticon photographs.
